-- District of Columbia
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'DC-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'DC Fire EMS protocol: CPR, defibrillation, ACLS medications.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'District of Columbia - Washington DC' AND c.state = 'District of Columbia' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
